name: Depth Tee
description:
Check your depth perception with our Depth tee - a funky update of the Monster Pocket tee. Tee has our friendly green monster perched on the chest, but is now featured with a new print that is sure to play eye tricks on anyone. A tee that's fun for kids and fun for adults!

Like all other Cay & Clue tees, the Depth tee makes a great gift for kids and adults! The lightweight fabric and creative print let you have fun while being fashionable and allow you to explore your imagination.

Depth tee is a heavyweight 50/50 blend of cotton and polyester. Tee has shoulder-to-shoulder taping, double-needle sleeves and bottom hem with side seamed body. Screen printed with green pocket monster on wearer's left chest and vertical depth perception lines printed in black across bottom half of tee. Cay & Clue logo printed on wearer's mid right. All printing is of high quality and durable for many washes.

name: Warster Tee
description:
Our Warster tee is featured here in black, with different contrast colors from those featured on our canvas tote. Inspired by Andy Warhol, these colorful little monsters will help brighten anyone's day!

One of our most popular prints, the Warster tee makes great gifts for friends and family of all ages!

Warster tee is made of 100% preshrunk cotton. Tee has seamless collar, taped neck and shoulders, cover-stitched neckline, double-needle sleeves and bottom hem, and is quarter turned for a more comfortable fit. Monster printed is screen printed on front for royal blue/cyan tee, and on back for green/royal blue tee. All printing is of high quality and durable for many washes.

name: LA Tourist Tee
description:
Take a tour of Los Angeles, monster style! Our friendly monster has once again made an appearance, although this time, he's sightseeing in LA! He's ready with his shades, and all he needs is a tourguide (you).

Know anyone who loves monsters? Or anyone who loves Los Angeles? This is the perfect tee for them! Or you! LA Tourist tee features monsters in two different colors: purple and green.

LA Tourist tee is made of 100% preshrunk cotton. Tee has seamless collar, taped neck and shoulders, cover-stitched neckline, double-needle sleeves and bottom hem, and is quarter turned for a more comfortable fit. Screen printed on front is graphic of Los Angeles, with monster roaming the city in the background. All printing is of high quality and durable for many washes.

name: University Tee
description:
The University tee is great for little ones as well as adults, as it helps people of all ages looking fresh and unique. =)

Should you decide to make this great tee a gift for someone, help them explore their imagination by asking them to find Cay and Clue on the shirt! Cay and Clue have each been worked into the design so they look like they are part of the crest. Tees are soft and comfortable; great for everyone. University tee is available in two colors: Black with white screen print, and white with black screen print.

University tee is made of 100% preshrunk cotton. Tee has seamless collar, taped neck and shoulders, cover-stitched neckline, double-needle sleeves and bottom hem, and is quarter turned for a more comfortable fit. Screen printed on front is Cay and Clue faux university crest. All printing is of high quality and durable for many washes.

name: Peeper Tee
description:
Brighten up the plain white tee classic with a friendly little monster peeping out at you! The Peeper tee depicts our resident monster enlarged and redesigned. Design is something kids will enjoy wearing, especially when they are the first of their friends to own one!

Our soft tees make great gifts for kids and adults! 

Peeper tee is a heavyweight 50/50 blend of cotton and polyester. Tee has shoulder-to-shoulder taping, double-needle sleeves and bottom hem with side seamed body. Screen printed with plastisol ink is part of a green monster peeping out from hem of shirt. All printing is of high quality and durable for many washes.
